{"id":2394,"date":"2019-11-19T16:20:46","date_gmt":"2019-11-19T09:20:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?post_type=product&#038;p=2394"},"modified":"2020-06-06T20:11:44","modified_gmt":"2020-06-06T13:11:44","slug":"mau-rem-cua-2-lop-sang-trong-cho-biet-thu-sieu-dep-tai-ninh-binh","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/mau-rem-cua-2-lop-sang-trong-cho-biet-thu-sieu-dep-tai-ninh-binh","title":{"rendered":"M\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp cao c\u1ea5p cho bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Ninh B\u00ecnh"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\"><strong>M\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp cao c\u1ea5p cho bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Ninh B\u00ecnh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">M\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp<\/span><\/a> l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ua chu\u1ed9ng, \u0111\u1eb7t mua t\u1ea1i c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">r\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh<\/span><\/a>. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t cho nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u00e1c nhau<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">M\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i 2 l\u1edbp t\u1ea1i Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u00fa H\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i t\u1ec9nh Ninh B\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi ng\u00f4i bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb9p l\u1ed9ng l\u1eaby c\u1ee7a ch\u00fa th\u00ec ch\u00fa \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1eabu r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c hai l\u1edbp cao c\u1ea5p si\u00eau b\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb9p l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t sang tr\u1ecdng<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f9ng chi\u00eam ngh\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m do ch\u00ednh <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh<\/span><\/a> thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 t\u1ea1i Ninh B\u00ecnh ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2413\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-19-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"rem-cua-2-lop-sang-trong\" width=\"1293\" height=\"1724\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-19-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-19-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-19-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-19-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-19.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1293px) 100vw, 1293px\" title=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><strong><em>Gam m\u00e0u ghi sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u1ed7i m\u1ed1t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2409\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-15-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"rem-cua-2-lop-cao-cap\" width=\"1277\" height=\"1702\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-15-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-15-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-15-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-15-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-15.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1277px) 100vw, 1277px\" title=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><strong><em>Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ec1n m\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 r\u1ee7 s\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb9p\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam:<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/nhung-luu-y-khi-lua-chon-rem-vai-cao-cap-dep\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\">Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i cao c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1eb9p<\/span><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2407\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-13-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"rem-cua-2-lop-tai-ninh-binh\" width=\"1265\" height=\"1687\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-13-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-13-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-13-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-13-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-13.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1265px) 100vw, 1265px\" title=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><strong><em>B\u1ed9 ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n thanh s\u01a1n t\u0129nh \u0111i\u1ec7n cao c\u1ea5p m\u00e0u xanh r\u00eau t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 130%;\"><strong>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><em><strong>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/strong><\/em><em><strong>?<\/strong><\/em><\/span> L\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c may ho\u1eb7c gia c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i voan, cotton, l\u1ee5a, nhung, v\u1ea3i th\u1ed5 c\u1ea9m,&#8230;T\u00f9y v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i may v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng hay may c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p m\u00e0 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch nhau. Ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecda ti\u1ebft v\u1ea3i l\u00e0m r\u00e8m c\u1eeda c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 phong ph\u00fa cho b\u1ea1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><em><strong>C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ki\u1ec3u may r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i n\u00e0o?<\/strong><\/em><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #333333;\">C<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u00f3 3 ki\u1ec3u may r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 may ly, may Ore, may x\u1ebfp l\u1edbp (roman). Ngo\u00e0i ra c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u may k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa 3 ki\u1ec3u ch\u00ednh nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 m\u1edbi l\u1ea1, ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch cho r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i.<\/span><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i may ki\u1ec3u ly: <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333; background: white;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i may ki\u1ec3u ly l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y ki\u1ec3u r\u00e8m n\u00e0y \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc, c\u01a1 quan hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi may r\u00e8m s\u1ebd ch\u1ee5m 1 \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ea3i l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng m\u00fai nh\u1ecf, t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng n\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng nh\u1ea5p nh\u00f4 tr\u00ean mi\u1ebfng v\u1ea3i. Phong c\u00e1ch may x\u1ebfp ly t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng v\u1ebb m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat cho r\u00e8m c\u1eeda n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau th\u00edch.<br \/>\n<\/span><strong><span style=\"color: #333333; background: white;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i may ki\u1ec3u Ore: <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333; background: white;\">May r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i ki\u1ec3u Ore l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch chia v\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng m\u00fai b\u1eb1ng nhau v\u00e0 may l\u1ea1i, sau \u0111\u00f3 treo l\u00ean thanh r\u00e8m. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch may hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap cho kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean sang tr\u1ecdng, thu h\u00fat h\u01a1n.<br \/>\n<\/span><strong><span style=\"color: #333333; background: white;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i ki\u1ec3u may x\u1ebfp l\u1edbp: <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333; background: white;\">Ki\u1ec3u may r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i x\u1ebfp l\u1edbp t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 chia t\u1ea5m v\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c \u0111o\u1ea1n b\u1eb1ng nhau,sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1edbt c\u00e1c ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4. Khi k\u00e9o r\u00e8m c\u00e1c \u00f4 v\u1ea3i s\u1ebd x\u1ebfp l\u00ean nhau, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfc qu\u1ea1t gi\u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng khi th\u1ea3 xu\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m r\u00e8m ph\u1eb3ng. Ki\u1ec3u r\u00e8m n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 r\u00e8m Roman.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0in; text-align: justify; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333333; background: white;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><em><strong>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i may r\u00e8m<br \/>\n<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333; background: white;\">V\u1ea3i Cotton: <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333; background: white;\">V\u1ea3i Cotton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb b\u00f4ng, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh mau kh\u00f4, h\u00fat \u1ea9m t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng. Nh\u1edd ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u gi\u1eef \u1ea5m t\u1ed1t v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng. l\u1ea1i m\u00e1t m\u1ebb v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00ean v\u1ea3i cotton v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng may qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o, v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng may r\u00e8m c\u1eeda. Ngo\u00e0i r\u00e8m may t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u cotton 100%, c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u cotton pha nilon c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn. V\u1ea3i cotton d\u1ec5 co r\u00fat v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 nh\u0103n h\u01a1n c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i kh\u00e1c, v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd trong kh\u00e2u gi\u1eb7t \u1ee7i v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n ch\u00fang.<br \/>\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">V\u1ea3i b\u1ed1<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">: Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi v\u1ea3i Cotton, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng ch\u01a1i, c\u00f3 \u00edt h\u1ecda ti\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc. Tuy v\u1ea3i b\u1ed1 mang v\u1ebb m\u1ed9c m\u1ea1c nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian c\u00f3 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 ki\u1ec3u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e2y. R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i b\u1ed1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n trong t\u1eebng n\u00e9t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i mang \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00e9t ri\u00eang kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i kh\u00e1c.<br \/>\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">V\u1ea3i voan<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">: V\u1ea3i voan m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng l\u00e0m l\u1edbp l\u00f3t trong c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i 2 l\u1edbp. R\u00e8m 2 l\u1edbp th\u01b0\u1eddng bao g\u1ed3m 1 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y v\u00e0 1 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i voan m\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ec3 trang tr\u00ed. V\u1ea3i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec n\u00f3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. Voan c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 voan nh\u0103n, voal hoa, voan th\u00eau,..cho b\u1ea1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br \/>\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">V\u1ea3i l\u1ee5a\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">: V\u1ea3i l\u1ee5a m\u1ecbn, m\u1ecfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb t\u01a1 t\u1eb1m n\u00ean r\u1ea5t nh\u1eb9. Lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng l\u00e0m r\u00e8m c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng, ng\u0103n \u00e1nh n\u1eafng chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 100%<br \/>\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">V\u1ea3i taffeta<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">: V\u1ea3i taffeta m\u1ecfng, c\u1ee9ng n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m v\u1ea3i may r\u00e8m m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i m\u00e0u tr\u00ean ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u r\u00e8m, hay hai bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m. V\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0u s\u1eafc gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00e9t ri\u00eang cho kh\u00f4ng gian.<br \/>\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">V\u1ea3i Satin<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">: V\u1ea3i Satin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb l\u1ee5a thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, mang l\u1ea1i n\u00e9t tr\u1ebb trung cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0. Tuy nhi\u00ean, lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng n\u00ean th\u00edch h\u1ee3p l\u00e0m r\u00e8m c\u1eeda cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 ho\u1eb7c ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1ebb nh\u1ecf. V\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i n\u00ean may c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ren \u0111i\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e0 v\u00e0 v\u1ea3i voan m\u1ecfng c\u00e0ng mang l\u1ea1i n\u00e9t quy\u1ebfn r\u0169. Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1ea3i cotton v\u1edbi v\u1ea3i Satin \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng.<br \/>\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">V\u1ea3i \u0111\u0169i<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">: V\u1ea3i \u0111\u0169i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 v\u1ea3i b\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5t m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn h\u01a1n. \u0110\u0169i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ec7t t\u1eeb s\u1ee3i n\u00ean r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 n\u00e9t thu h\u00fat kh\u00f3 t\u1ea3. V\u1ea3i \u0111\u0169i th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m c\u1eeda bu\u00f4ng r\u1ee7, t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng.<br \/>\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">V\u1ea3i nhung<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">: V\u1ea3i nhung d\u00e0y n\u1eb7ng l\u1ea1i m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i trang tr\u00ed ho\u00e0ng cung v\u00e0 c\u00e1c n\u01a1i sang tr\u1ecdng t\u1eeb th\u1eddi x\u01b0a. C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i nhung l\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1ch \u00e2m, c\u1ea3n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1t n\u00ean r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0.\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0in; text-align: justify; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 90%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #333333; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Mua r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh<br \/>\n<\/strong>V\u1edbi ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n<a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/\">\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh<\/span><\/a>\u00a0lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, uy t\u00edn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp s\u1ebd c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 giao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean t\u1eeb 650,000 \u2013 1,850,000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/m ngang ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n. C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi d\u00f2ng v\u1ea3i cao c\u1ea5p nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u t\u1eeb\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-vai-cao-cap\/\">B\u1ec9, \u0110\u00e0i Loan, Nh\u1eadt<\/a><\/span>\u00a0th\u00ec gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, Kho\u1ea3ng 2,300,000 \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean. C\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng nh\u00e1i, h\u00e0ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00ean R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c, xu\u1ea5t s\u1ee9 r\u00f5 d\u00e0ng. Cam k\u1ebft ho\u00e0n ti\u1ec1n 100% khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng nh\u00e1i hay s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh cung c\u1ea5p lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb h\u01a1n 10-20% th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ngo\u00e0i ra,\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/\">R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh<\/a><\/span>\u00a0c\u00f2n cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gi\u1eb7t l\u00e0 cho b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m th\u00eam m\u1edbi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. \u0110\u0103ng K\u00fd gi\u1eb7t l\u00e0:\u00a00984342228<\/span><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">V\u1edbi 10 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 k\u1ef9 s\u01b0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, th\u1ee3 r\u00e8m c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 tay ngh\u1ec1 cao,\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/\">R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh<\/a><\/span>\u00a0lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong ng\u00e0nh r\u00e8m c\u1eeda. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u tr\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1eeb \u0110\u00e0i Loan, Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u1ea3i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Th\u00e1i Lan,\u2026 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c kho v\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u1ec9nh tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u1ee7ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, phong ph\u00fa nh\u01b0: b\u1ed1, nhung, g\u1ea5m, th\u00f4,\u00a0 \u0111\u0169i, cotton,\u2026 C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9<strong>m<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m ra v\u1edbi kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn, \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eabu m\u00e3 v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7ng lo\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng qua b\u1ea5t k\u00ec trung gian n\u00e0o n\u00ean lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1ea5 \u2013 uy t\u00edn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u:\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/cua-hang\/rem-hai-lop\/rem-2-lop-sang-trong-cho-biet-thu-tai-quang-ninh\/\">R\u00e8m 2 l\u1edbp sang tr\u1ecdng cho bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh<\/a>,<a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/cua-hang\/rem-biet-thu\/rem-vai-cao-cap-cho-biet-thu-sieu-dep-tai-cau-giay-ha-noi\/\">\u00a0R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i cao c\u1ea5p cho bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i,\u2026<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">H\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu kho c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p, sang tr\u1ecdng, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean s\u1ebd t\u1eadn t\u00e2m v\u1edbi ngh\u1ec1, s\u1ebd \u0111em t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec tinh t\u00fay nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u2013 Uy t\u00edn qu\u00fd h\u01a1n h\u00e0ng, n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">M\u1ecdi chi ti\u1ebft xin li\u00ean h\u1ec7<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 90%;\"><strong>C\u00d4NG TY TNHH TH\u01af\u01a0NG M\u1ea0I &amp; N\u1ed8I TH\u1ea4T PH\u00da TH\u00c0NH<\/strong>\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><em>Showroom<\/em>: s\u1ed1 160 Khu\u1ea5t Duy Ti\u1ebfn \u2013 Thanh Xu\u00e2n \u2013 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><em>\u0110i\u